## [2026-02-05] C# Proxy API Gitignore
## Root-level configuration for API, Tests, and Benchmark projects.

# --- .NET / Visual Studio ---
# Ignore build artifacts and temporary files
bin/
obj/
out/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

# Visual Studio per-user files and cache
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.suo

# --- Secrets and Configuration (CRITICAL FOR PROXY) ---
# Do not commit sensitive credentials or production settings.
# Use environment variables or Key Vaults for production secrets.
appsettings.Production.json
appsettings.Staging.json
secrets.json
*.pfx
*.publishsettings

# --- NuGet Packages ---
# Packages are restored during the build process
*.nupkg
**/packages/*
!**/packages/build/
project.lock.json
project.assets.json

# --- Testing and Code Coverage ---
# Artifacts from xUnit/NUnit and coverage tools like Coverlet
TestResults/
*.sequenced.json
coverage/
*.lcov
*.coverage

# --- BenchmarkDotNet ---
# Specialized for the performance project. Ignore generated source and results.
**/BenchmarkDotNet.Artifacts/

# --- Docker ---
# Ignore docker-specific build contexts
.dockerignore
**/obj/Docker/

# --- Logs and Diagnostics ---
# Standard log files and crash dumps
*.log
*.eventlog
logs/
*.stackdump

# --- Operating System ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
